author: Lobo_da_boss_
title: My first experience with the updated Olaf
review:
Opening;

The Olaf keyring is a fun one and is my first personal experience with the new variant of the character released last year .

The Minifigure -

The Minifigure has the standard mould for Olafs head , an orange unicorn horn for his carrot nose and the moulded torso and legs with printing and Minidoll arms in redish brown .

In conclusion -

this is a nice keyring and I have no complaints it is just good so I recommend it .
